data.description: Great opportunity in Mt. Vernon School District. 4 bedroom home. 2 and 1/2 baths. New roof. Updated kitchen and open floor plan. Spacious backyard with lots of potential. Home offers lots of space for entertaining. Cozy dining room that could be used for an office or extra seating space. Conveniently located between I-70 and Geist. Great opportunity to purchase a home under $300k in this growing community.
